text: Brooks, Meadows and Lovely Faces (, translit. Brooks, Meadows and Lovely Faces) is a 2016 Egyptian comedy movie directed by Yousry Nasrallah and starring Laila Eloui, Bassem Samra, Menna Shalabi. ==Other websites== * Category:2016 comedy movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:Movies directed by Yousry Nasrallah
title: Brooks, Meadows and Lovely Faces
